❤️ This was emotional to put into words, but to @DeAngeloWilliams and @Risalyn34: After my 2 best friends passed away in a 3-year span, life was really hard. During that time, no one brought me more moments of joy than you and your AMAZING kids, and I just want to say that I love you all so much and thank you from the bottom of my heart. 

While I’ve always loved and appreciated you, seeing you all for the first time in years Tuesday night at DeAngelo’s College Football Hall of Fame induction made me feel this huge wave of gratitude for all that you guys did for me—the countless FaceTimes, invitations, and love, all of which forced me to smile and laugh at a time when I really didn’t feel like it. Now that I’m happy and in a great place in my life, I am so glad I can express all of the above and below to you. ❤️

To DeAngelo: Our relationship started as you being one of my 1st clients, and your trust and belief in my vision for helping you build your brand led to fun and mutually beneficial experiences for us, but you are so much more than a client to me. You are family, and your family is family. Seeing you get inducted into the College Football Hall of Fame made me feel pure joy for you, knowing how hard you worked at your craft, despite often getting overlooked. I know that your Mom was watching down on you with a huge smile on her face 👼🏿❤️

To Risalyn: You are the real MVP (sorry, DeAngelo haha). I was always well aware that you were the one behind the countless videos and birthday cards from the kids, FaceTimes pretending that the kids did it on their own (c’mon Ris, I’m not that dumb hahaha), and just always thinking of ways to have those amazing little ones make me laugh. 

To Rhiya, Reyna, DJ, and Decker: You are such special kids and mean so much to me. Seeing you Tuesday made my heart feel so full, and I just thank you for being the sweet, kind, and loving little humans that you are. I promise that one day my future kids will return the favor and be there to bring you moments of joy when you need it, because that’s the circle of life and what family is for.

I love you guys so so much, and from the bottom of my heart, thank you for being you. ❤️❤️
